        [
          "Staff Generated History"
        ],
        [
          "You are a created creature by the Tremere, made from the bodies of captured members of the Sabbat. The problem though, is that the ritual has weakened over the centuries. You still hear the memories from the lives of those that made you, The hunger, the hate, the desire to kill. The Tremere have put you in a situation to distract you:  you guard a group of captured Vampires under the sea. You are their sole guardian. As the conflict in the city has grown, the Tremere have had you start comming to court to defend the them. They don't know how unstable you are, though."
